&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a Deployment Strategist to operate at the intersection of product and sales. You will be responsible for driving deals forward and making Dirac real inside the customer environment. You will own the technical and operational side of enterprise engagements, from early discovery through deployment, working directly with customers to map their systems, structure the engagement, and push adoption.&lt;/p&gt;
