&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the technical and operational execution of enterprise deals alongside Account Executives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Architect customer engagements from discovery through deployment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Map customer organizations, identify stakeholders, and understand internal dynamics&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translate engineering and manufacturing workflows into concrete implementations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Push customers toward infrastructure-level adoption within their existing stack&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define timelines, scope level of effort, and create urgency to move deals forward&lt;/li&gt;
