&lt;li&gt;Manage early deployments to ensure successful rollout and adoption&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build clear materials including decks, process flows, and system diagrams to communicate solutions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner closely with product and engineering to relay insights from the field&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
