&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3+ years of experience in consulting, deployment, or similar roles&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working with engineering, manufacturing, or hardware-focused organizations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong ability to understand technical systems and translate them into business impact&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven ability to operate in ambiguous, fast-paced environments and drive outcomes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;High ownership mindset with a bias toward action&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
