&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build integrations between BuildOS and customer systems (PLM, ERP, etc.)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify and fix high-impact issues blocking customer adoption&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ship deployment-critical features with speed and quality&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Review code and help reduce PR backlog across the engineering team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with product and core engineering to prioritize high-leverage work&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support pilots, deployments, and customer technical needs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate in demos and technical discussions as needed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Qualifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong full-stack software engineering fundamentals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to write production-quality code in modern languages (e.g. React, TypeScript, Go)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working in complex systems and codebases&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to quickly understand and debug unfamiliar systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong communication skills in technical and customer-facing contexts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;High ownership and bias toward action&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with APIs, integrations, and distributed systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with CAD / PLM / ERP ecosystems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in high-growth startup environments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfort with AI-assisted development workflows&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
